lyrics.line: Is this thing on? Can you hear me?
I've been in showbiz for quite some time,
And I'm still kicking, feeling just fine
My humor may be a little risqué,
But that's just how I like to play
I've lived a life full of laughter and love,
And I thank my fans, up above
So here's to all the comedians out there,
Keep making people laugh, if you dare
Just remember to always be true to yourself,
And never put your talent on the shelf
It's been fun, but now it's time for me
Thanks for listening and have a great day,
Betty White signing off in her own special way
